{"tid":1542673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[四方西澄清]劉慧卿:紐約時報報導不正確，沒有得悉民主派支持中央欽點邱騰華","createTime":"2019-09-05T02:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:37:48.000Z","uid":78519,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f5a40db62b58f2ee5d6ed7d14fb246877dc4c7","tid":1542673,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"澄清聲明:<br />\n紐約時報中文網 報導: 前民主黨主席 劉慧卿 說民主派人士希望北京選擇曾擔任環境局局長，現任商務及經濟發展局局長 邱騰華 為行政長官。報導不正確 因為我從沒有說過這些話。<br />\n<br />\n我在8月20日早上 在外國記者會遇到 紐約時報記者 Keith Bradshaw, 在簡談中提及 數名傳媒報導 可能成為行政長官的人選，包括邱騰華。<br />\n<br />\n我從沒有得悉民主派人士希望北京選擇邱為行政長官，更沒有資格代表民主派就此事發言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbZQJvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbZQJvY.jpg&h=e119bf99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10217517663028307&amp;set=a.1373083081971&amp;type=3&amp;eid=ARBfEFj_thNmR699qVvl7D1uDbf5ELDblrdpkb5PgB7FvoKZZ2C7zm5B6Tq5GBQGVZMmYk6TM-kPDnwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10217517663028307%26set%3Da.1373083081971%26type%3D3%26eid%3DARBfEFj_thNmR699qVvl7D1uDbf5ELDblrdpkb5PgB7FvoKZZ2C7zm5B6Tq5GBQGVZMmYk6TM-kPDnwY&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=13491613\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10217517663028307&amp;set=a.1373083081971&amp;type=3&amp;eid=ARBfEFj_thNmR699qVvl7D1uDbf5ELDblrdpkb5PgB7FvoKZZ2C7zm5B6Tq5GBQGVZMmYk6TM-kPDnwY</a>"},{"pid":"34a6ede6b98691228ac4ae238946459f2da5cb40","tid":1542673,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"831 cctv"},{"pid":"33850e6c300a04097aaed95bb0e2673ca51d3785","tid":1542673,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"你個Emily<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6748fc36d1fd2c0ba7c632a6996b0b8826524d7","tid":1542673,"uid"